OL,7,FNobel Prize-winning author Abdulrazak
OL,8,FGurnah has said he did not pick
OL,9,Fliterature as an A-level as it did not
OL,10,Ffeel "useful".
OL,12,FThe Tanzanian author, who was awarded
OL,13,Fthe Nobel Prize for literature in
OL,14,F2021, was born in 1948 on the island
OL,15,Fof Zanzibar, now part of Tanzania, and
OL,16,Fmoved to Britain as a refugee in 1968,
OL,17,Ffleeing a repressive regime that
OL,18,Fpersecuted the Arab Muslim community
OL,19,Fto which he belonged.
