OL,4,Cliterature A-level as it did not feel
OL,5,C'useful'
OL,7,FSpeaking on BBC Radio 4's Desert
OL,8,FIsland Discs, he said: "We grew up
OL,9,Fduring the campaign for
OL,10,Fdecolonisation, and it was kind of
OL,11,Fdrummed into us, and perhaps it didn't
OL,12,Fneed that much drumming, that if you
OL,13,Fget an opportunity to study, then you
OL,14,Fmust do something that's going to be
OL,15,Fuseful to your country. Whoever
OL,16,Fthought that reading literature was
OL,17,Fgoing to be useful to anybody?
