OL,3,CNobel Prize author did not pick
OL,4,Cliterature A-level as it did not feel
OL,5,C'useful'
OL,7,F"So, really, we were all kind of being
OL,8,Fled towards either doing science
OL,9,Fsubjects, if you got the opportunity,
OL,10,For possibly law or something like
OL,11,Fthat. And so when we came here, we
OL,12,Fchose to do A-levels in those
OL,13,Fsubjects. I worked pretty hard,
OL,14,Fespecially when my cousin was still
OL,15,Fhere with us, and he just made sure we
OL,16,Fwe did all the homework."
