OL,4,Cliterature A-level as it did not feel
OL,5,C'useful'
OL,7,FHe later changed courses to study
OL,8,Fliterature and took evening classes,
OL,9,Fgoing on to obtain a Bachelor of
OL,10,FEducation from Christ Church college
OL,11,FCanterbury and then a PhD.
OL,13,FGurnah added: "I thought, this is what
OL,14,FI should have done from the beginning.
OL,15,FI should not have listened to that
OL,16,Fhectoring voice that was saying, be
OL,17,Fsomething useful. I should have done
OL,18,Fthis because this is something I get
OL,19,Fpleasure from doing and that I know I
OL,20,Fcan do well."
