OL,5,C'useful'
OL,7,F"The first thing I thought when I was
OL,8,Fon my own after having been picked up
OL,9,Ffrom the airport by the cousin and
OL,10,Ftaken to the place where we were
OL,11,Fstaying, and I was lying in bed and
OL,12,Fthinking, 'What have I done?'"
OL,14,FIt was another 17 years before he was
OL,15,Fable to see his family again, after
OL,16,Fleaving his parents and four siblings
OL,17,Fto study in Britain, and paid for the
OL,18,Fflight using insurance money he
OL,19,Freceived for a roof leak in his house
OL,20,Fin Balham, stuffing the hole in the
OL,21,Fceiling with newspaper.
