OL,7,FIn the episode, which asks guests to
OL,8,Fshare the soundtrack to their lives,
OL,9,FGurnah selected a range of music
OL,10,Fincluding songs from his Zanzibar
OL,11,Fheritage, the Beatles and Hit The Road
OL,12,FJack by Ray Charles.
OL,14,FHis fifth song for the programme was
OL,15,FThe Beatles' A Day In The Life, which
OL,16,Fhe explained reminds him of his first
OL,17,FChristmas in the UK after a family
OL,18,Fhosted him and his brother.
