OL,3,CNobel Prize author did not pick
OL,4,Cliterature A-level as it did not feel
OL,5,C'useful'
OL,7,FHe said: "We were invited to spend
OL,8,FChristmas day, our first Christmas in
OL,9,FEngland with this family, if I
OL,10,Fremember correctly, there was two sons
OL,11,Fand a daughter. The eldest son was
OL,12,Fpossibly about 18 or 19, something
OL,13,Flike and one of his presents was
OL,14,FSergeant Pepper. And so he put it on
OL,15,Fin a record player. And so that's the
OL,16,Ffirst time I heard this, but every
OL,17,Ftime I listened to this opening, I
OL,18,Fremember that family and that
OL,19,FChristmas."
